      <h1>The departments of the Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion</h1> 
      <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
       <div class="pageDescription"><h4>&nbsp;</h4> </div>       
    </div>
    
               
        
    
    <div id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_divPageContent" class="documentBody">
    
       
    
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/organisation/departments/Department-Of-Children-and-Youth-Policy.html?id=81" title="">
                    Department Of Children and Youth Policy
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                This department is responsible for developing and coordinating the Ministry's policies toward children and youth, including subsidy programmes to benefit children’s and youth organizations, international youth exchanges and services for children and youth in urban environments.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/organisation/departments/Department-of-Consumer-Affairs.html?id=83" title="">
                    Department of Consumer Affairs
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The responsibilities of this department include consumer policy, consumer information, household economics, sustainable consumption and consumer research. 

            </p>
            
        </div>
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/organisation/departments/the-department-of-integration-and-divers.html?id=589415" title="">
                    Department of Integration and Diversity
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The Department of Integration and Diversity (IMA) works on policies relating to integration and diversity, both vis-à-vis immigrants and the population in general. The Department is responsible for coordinating policies relating to the disabled.

            </p>
            
        </div>
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/organisation/departments/department-of-family-affairs-and-gender-.html?id=82" title="">
                    Department of Family Affairs and Equality
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                This department oversees public policies promoting equality with regard to gender and sexual orientation. It is also responsible for developing family-life and cohabitation policies as well as legislation affecting children and families.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/organisation/departments/information-secretariat.html?id=87086" title="">
                    Departement of Communications
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The Ministry of Children and Equality is committed to openness. It takes a proactive approach to informational work, publishing accurate information in a timely fashion and providing updated reports at www.bld.dep.no/english  Media inquiries and requests for information are dealt with on an ongoing basis.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/bld/BLD-arbeider-for-at/organisation/departments/Department-of-Planning-and-Administration.html?id=84" title="">
                    Department of Planning and Administration
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                This department oversees service and support activities for the rest of the Ministry. It manages personnel and organizational issues.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    
 
   
    </div>              
       
